snippet.title: Fifa 96 - SEGA  Saturn - Intro and  Gameplay
snippet.description: Don't listen to the knockers, this is a great football game with tons of playability and in 1996 was an amazing football game  with fab gfx and stunning music and of course for the 1st time in a Football game (not NFL) play by play commentary by John Motson , much like SEGA's amazing Joe II on the Mega Drive
